# tour-drc: run DRC on a real SKY130 cell, the violations list fills, then click a
# violation and the canvas zooms to its marker. The feature reads within the first
# two seconds: the list is populated before the first capture frame.
viewport 1600x1000
use-case inspect-cell
settle
run-drc
wait 6
capture 45 20
select-violation 0
zoom-violation
wait 4
capture 55 20
